{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/137", "repo": "rails", "body": "I added some commits as you suggest but I'm not really happy with this approach. It has several code smells:\n\n* AD::Callbacks has 3-4 responsibilities: preparation, reloading, before/after callbacks -- SRP violation.\n* A boolean flag (prepare_each_request/development_mode) that affects control flow in a non-trivial manner.\n* Increased coupling in the assumption that development mode = !config.cache_classes = prepare_each_request.\n\nhttps://github.com/bigfix/rails/commit/a83b36a7cb162a711b4e0c9cec1433f16c0b8328#commitcomment-221642", "_id": {"$oid": "523868afbd3543c1510129bb"}, "issue_id": 137, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/623223", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/137#issuecomment-623223", "updated_at": "2010-12-19T22:39:31Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jfirebaugh/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jfirebaugh/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jfirebaugh/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jfirebaugh/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jfirebaugh", "login": "jfirebaugh", "gravatar_id": "a82409021ddf415a8027872b889c5f74", "html_url": "https://github.com/jfirebaugh", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jfirebaugh/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jfirebaugh/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jfirebaugh/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/a82409021ddf415a8027872b889c5f74?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F9db597035f77a6c1167e05ca916801fa.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jfirebaugh/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 98601, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jfirebaugh/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2010-12-19T22:39:00Z", "id": 623223, "owner": "rails"}
